<div class="container-fluid">
  <img src="https://s3.amazonaws.com/static.bitly.com/graphics/blog/2013/10/map+no+legend.png" width="800px">
</div>

  <div class="crime-categories row">

  <div class="col-md-8 col-md-offset-2">

    <div class="row">
      <div class="col-md-4">
        <%= image_tag "icon-murder.png" %>
        <p class="category-title">Murder</p>
        <p>The willful (non-negligent) killing of one human being by another.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="col-md-4">
        <%= image_tag "icon-manslaughter.png" %>
        <p class="category-title">Manslaughter</p>
        <p>The killing of another person through gross negligence.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="col-md-4">
        <%= image_tag "icon-sexual-assault-f.png" %>
        <p class="category-title">Sexual Assault - Forcible</p>
        <p>Any sexual act directed against another person, forcibly and/or against that person's will; or not forcibly or against the person's will where the victim is incapable of giving consent.</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="row">
      <div class="col-md-4">
        <%= image_tag "icon-sexual-assault-nonforcible.png" %>
        <p class="category-title">Sexual Assault - Nonforcible</p>
        <p>Unlawful, non-forcible sexual intercourse.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="col-md-4">
        <%= image_tag "icon-robbery.png" %>
        <p class="category-title">Robbery</p>
        <p>The taking or attempting to take anything of value from the care, custody, or control of a person or persons by force or threat of force or violence and/or by putting the victim in fear.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="col-md-4">
        <%= image_tag "icon-aggravated-assault.png" %>
        <p class="category-title">Aggravated Assault</p>
        <p>An unlawful attack by one person upon another for the purpose of inflicting severe or aggravated bodily injury. This type of assault usually is accompanied by the use of a weapon or by means likely to produce death or great bodily harm.</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="row">
      <div class="col-md-4">
        <%= image_tag "icon-burglary.png" %>
        <p class="category-title">Burglary</p>
        <p>The unlawful entry of a structure to commit a felony or a theft.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="col-md-4">
        <%= image_tag "icon-motor-vehicle-theft.png" %>
        <p class="category-title">Motor Vehicle Theft</p>
        <p>The theft or attempted theft of a motor vehicle.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="col-md-4">
        <%= image_tag "icon-arson.png" %>
        <p class="category-title">Arson</p>
        <p>Any willful or malicious burning or attempt to burn, with or without intent to defraud, a dwelling house, public building, motor vehicle or aircraft, personal property of another, etc.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
</div>